| Files |
___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

   |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-Classes		| Any Classes Go Here
   |	-php/			| PHP Classes
   |	  --Database.php			| DatabaseConnection class
   |	  --Filters.php				| User input filtering class
   |	  --htmLawed1.1.9.1.php		| Html Sanitizer ( http://www.bioinformatics.org/phplabware/internal_utilities/htmLawed/ )
   |	  --Post.php				| A Class representing a set of related html elements that serve a certain purpose (blog post, static page, game, video, etc...)
   |	  --Security.php				| User Authentication Check
   |	  --Template.php			| Allows for seperation of data gathering and presentation logic
   |	  --User.php				| Class for user management
   |	-js/				| JavaScript Classes
   |	  --mootools*core.js			| the MooTools core
   |	  --mootools*more.js		| the MooTools more
   |	  --DeepLinker.js			| adds a hash listener and caching system for deeplinking ajax content
   |	  --Lightbox.js				| adds "toggleable" layers to the page
   |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-docs/			| Documentation
   |	-jsDocs/				| JavaScript Documentation - Generated by jsdoc-toolkit - http://code.google.com/p/jsdoc-toolkit/
   |	-phpDocs/			| PHP Documentation - Generated by phpDocumentor - http://www.phpdoc.org/
   |--index.php			| page displaying iframes with phpDocs, jsDocs, and screenshot of MooKit.dia
   |--MooKit.dia			| MooKit Dia diagram
   |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-img/			| images
   |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-js/			| JavaScript
   |--auth.js			| containes authorized area JavaScript
   |--debug.js			| on screen slide-up debugging box
   |--login.js			| creates login lightbox layer
   |--main.js			| global JavaScript
   |--postEdit.js			| ajax post editing
   |--signup.js			| creates signup lightbox layer
   |--userCSS.js			| ajax CSS style adding
   |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-logs/			| Error logs
   |--DBerrors.og		| MySQL Errors
   |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-php/			| PHP Scripts
   |--auth.php			| auth area content loading
   |--authUpdate.php	| calls the function in auth.php
   |--functions.php		| global site functions
   |--includes.php		| class includes and session initialization
   |--login.php			| simple php login script using the User and Database classes
   |--logout.php			| remove authentication
   |--postGet.php		| get post data
   |--postUpdate.php	| update a post
   |--signup.php		| simple php signup script using the User and Database classes
   |--test{1,2,3}.php		| sample php scripts for testing
   |--userCSS.php		| filter user entered CSS and send back to javascript for adding to document head
   |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-SQL/			| for reference: CREATE SQL statements needed for site database
   |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-style/			| CSS Styles
   |--content.css.php	| Content
   |--debug.css.php		| Debug
   |--loginForm.css.php	| Login Lightbox
   |--nav.css.php		| Menu
   |--post.css.php		| Post Display
   |--postEdit.css.php	| Post Edit
   |--signupForm.css.php	| Signup Lightbox
   |--style.php			| Global Styles
   |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |-templates/		| Page Templates
   |--content.tpl.php		| Main content
   |--loginForm.tpl.php	| Login Lightbox
   |--main.tpl.php		| Main template - All other templates are sub to main -
   |--nav.tpl.php		| Menu
   |--post.tpl.php		| Post Display
   |--postEdit.tpl.php		| Post Edit
   |--signupForm.tpl.php	| Signup Lightbox
   |--userCSS.tpl.php		| User Entered CSS Form
   |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |--index.php		| main site
   |--README		| this file
